docs.text: Getting Started Generator is a Laravel-based open-source toolkit for building basic needs for administration interface setup like Create, Read, Update, and Delete. It's the minimalistic template or a starting point for developing CMS system, admin panel, or any other web application that requires CRUD functionality. Requirements All you need is Composer and PHP ^8.1 . What's included Laravel - ^9.x Laravel Forify - ^1.x Laravel Debugbar - ^3.x Spatie permission - ^5.x Yajra datatable - ^10.x Intervention Image - ^2.x Mazer template - ^2.x Generator - ^0.1.x
